; Example that uses the `_` transpose command to simplify chords.
;
; This example produces identical output to `chords.mml`.

#Title Chords using transpose example

@1 piano

ABC @1

;; Major triad
A _+0
B _+4
C _+7
ABC o4 c d e f g a b r

;; Minor triad
A _+0
B _+3
C _+7
ABC o4 c d e f g a b r

;; Augmented triad
A _+0
B _+4
C _+8
ABC o4 c d e f g a b r

; Reset transpose
ABC _+0

